[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一周以后，辰星扭伤的脚已经完全恢复。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这天我来到休息大厅，发现辰星在一个安静的角落里，正拿着一本书读着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-1",
        "Flag": "b-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "b-1-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不动声色来到她的对面坐下",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女捋着耳畔银色的发丝，忽然注意到我的到来，抬起头来，眼眸明显有着欢欣之色。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "听说你到处在找我？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我才忙完一个任务回来，就从卡罗琳那得到了消息。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "说话的时候，我的目光扫过她拿着的书本。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "精致的书皮上刻着几个形体飞扬的大字——《呼啦啦小魔女》。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "辰星察觉到我的目光，脸颊微微红了红，不过没有掩饰书名，认真点头道。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员……我已经好了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可以去了？辰星说的那个地方？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这一周的时间，我一有空就带着辰星去尝试新的东西，给她各种新奇体验，而在中间的某天，辰星忽然找到我说，等她彻底恢复后，有个地方想邀请我一起去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我当然是答应了下来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过……不是今天。我想周六的时候，再和分析员一起……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "周六，休息日吗？也挺好的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我并没有多想，而辰星在我答应后，嘴角自然流露出欣喜的笑容，然后她像是想到了什么，将她手边一个精致的小食盒推了过来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "食盒里装着的是我没见过的小点心。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这些都是朔州的特产，我一直想试试，但之前没有机会，前几天我托人买到了，想和分析员一起尝尝。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她认真看着我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好吃的点心……一人独享自然是美味的，可是两个人一起享受，有着更美好的滋味。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那我就恭敬不如从命了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员不让我说谢谢，怎么和我说这种话啦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这不是多和你学了些朔州的话，得多用用熟悉嘛……唔……这个挺好吃的，你尝尝。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我说完后，看着少女含羞带怯，微微张起的粉唇，愣了愣后，笑着夹起那块糕点，递到她的嘴边。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "时间很快到了周六，我在公司的楼下等着辰星。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可惜的是天公不作美，今天天气不算太好，还没出门就开始下起了小雨，我特意带了把伞出门。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，你怎么……来这么早。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "现在是早上九点。距离我们约好的九点半，还隔着整整半个小时。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我不来早些，难道让你在这里干等半小时吗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "前一周出门与辰星汇合时，少女每次都是早早在指定的位置等我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "凝视着目光盈盈的辰星，我撑起伞，往外面走了一步。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "既然提前到了，干脆现在就出门吧，不过这个时间点会不会太早？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不会。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那就走吧。对了，外面在下雨，你有带伞吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她顿了顿，垂着眸光，不敢直视我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "正当我疑惑时，辰星才小声开口。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我，我出门的时候没怎么看天气……忘记带伞啦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我很难形容，听到这句话从辰星口中说出时，在我的内心窜动过怎样的心绪。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但我切实感觉到一种滚烫的温度，完全盖住了雨天微微的凉意，自我的胸膛不断浮现，甚至开始向我的灵魂蔓延。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……是吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我凝视着少女有些心虚的模样，而后者虽然看上去心虚，可还是坚定地给了我答复。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……是的！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那就没办法了。不过我这把伞足够大，两个人一起撑着也没问题的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那太好了！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们心照不宣，谁都没有提起坐车、再花些时间去多拿一把伞的话题。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我用右手撑着伞，辰星在我的左边。这是稍微有些别扭的姿势，但我觉得……这是最好的选择。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "虽然这次雨中的漫步，我不是背着辰星，可对我而言，这一刻与她的距离，好像更加的接近。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在往前走的时候，谁都没有说一句话，没有提过一个字。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "也许是一次“精心设计”的试探，",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "也许是一次“蓄谋已久”的意外，",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不知道哪一次晃动着手掌的时候，我的左手和辰星的右手相互触碰在了一起。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这一刻，我的心脏和呼吸都好似停拍。身体和灵魂都被某种滚烫的东西填充，让我几乎忘记了生存的本能。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这一触即分的触碰，也像是点燃了情绪的火苗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "难以遏制，无法压抑，积蓄的情感就这样迸发。就像铁会被磁力吸引，自然而然地向着彼此奔赴。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "于是——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "手指交错，",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "掌心相合。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "两只手紧紧抓在一起……不再松开。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "辰星有些不知道自己何时清醒过来的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她站在高台上，定定凝视着不久前被紧紧抓住的手掌。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "属于分析员的温度，仿佛还残留在她的指尖，一点点浸入她的身体，渗透她的灵魂。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "10、9、8——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "高台下忽然响起倒计时的声音，让辰星一个激灵。她像是从一场梦中苏醒，这才发现自己置身于一座高台。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这里是双人闯关活动的最后一关——也是这次她专门邀请分析员的目的地。在这之前，两人心心相印，息息相通，轻松突破了其他关卡的阻碍。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 73,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "辰星背对着赛道，站在高台的边缘。按照活动的规则，在最后一关的闯关中，分析员需要在规定的时间内闯过赛道，来到她所在的高台下，做好接住她的准备。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 74,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而她在倒计时为零的那一刻，就该从高台的边缘背对着赛道，往后仰倒。如果能被分析员接在怀中，就算获胜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 75,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "整个过程，参赛双方都不能有任何的交流。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 76,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是信任与羁绊的游戏。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 77,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "辰星凝望着不远处巨大的倒计时。在这单独的赛道，她听不到其他人的声音，也看不到分析员是否抵达终点。",
